Package de.fmp.liulab.core

Class ProteinStructureManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fmp.liulab.core.ProteinStructureManager
  • public class ProteinStructureManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Class responsible for creating PyMOL script (*.pml file) and calling software to be executed This class was adapted from CyToStruct, a Cytoscape app that makes a bridge between molecular viewers and Cytoscape (doi: 10.1016/j.str.2015.02.013)
    Author:
    diogobor
